<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/school_header') %>
    <main>
        <section class="infrastructure-hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Our State-of-the-Art Infrastructure</h1>
                <p>Providing a conducive and modern learning environment for every student.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="infrastructure-overview-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Facilities Designed for Excellence</h2>
                <p>N.R.K. Public School is equipped with modern infrastructure that supports a dynamic and engaging educational experience. We believe that a well-resourced environment is crucial for fostering curiosity, creativity, and academic achievement. Our facilities are designed to cater to the diverse needs of our students, ensuring their all-round development.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="facility-details-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 facility-item">
                        <img src="/images/facility-classroom.svg" alt="Smart Classrooms" class="facility-icon">
                        <h3>Smart Classrooms</h3>
                        <p>Our classrooms are spacious, well-lit, and equipped with smart boards and projectors, transforming traditional teaching into an interactive and engaging experience. This technology-enabled learning environment enhances comprehension and participation.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 facility-item">
                        <img src="/images/facility-lab.svg" alt="Science and Computer Labs" class="facility-icon">
                        <h3>Advanced Laboratories</h3>
                        <p>We have well-equipped Science (Physics, Chemistry, Biology) and Computer Laboratories that provide hands-on experience and foster experimental learning. Students can explore scientific principles and develop essential technical skills in a safe and supervised setting.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 facility-item">
                        <img src="/images/facility-library.svg" alt="Library" class="facility-icon">
                        <h3>Rich Library</h3>
                        <p>Our school boasts a vast library stocked with a wide range of books, magazines, and digital resources. It serves as a knowledge hub, encouraging students to cultivate reading habits and conduct research, expanding their horizons beyond textbooks.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 facility-item">
                        <img src="/images/facility-playground.svg" alt="Sports Facilities" class="facility-icon">
                        <h3>Sports and Recreation</h3>
                        <p>A sprawling playground and dedicated sports facilities for various indoor and outdoor games ensure that students have ample opportunities for physical activity, teamwork, and healthy competition. We encourage participation in sports for overall well-being.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 facility-item">
                        <img src="/images/facility-computer.svg" alt="Auditorium and Activity Rooms" class="facility-icon">
                        <h3>Auditorium and Activity Rooms</h3>
                        <p>The school has a well-furnished auditorium for cultural events, seminars, and performances. Additionally, various activity rooms are available for music, dance, art, and other co-curricular activities, fostering creative expression.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 facility-item">
                        <img src="/images/facility-transport.svg" alt="Transportation" class="facility-icon">
                        <h3>Safe Transportation</h3>
                        <p>Our fleet of well-maintained school buses, equipped with GPS tracking and supervised by trained staff, ensures safe and comfortable transportation for students commuting from various parts of Jamui and surrounding areas.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="call-to-action">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Explore Our Campus</h2>
                <p>Visit N.R.K. Public School to see our facilities firsthand and learn more about what we offer.</p>
                <a href="/school/contact" class="cta-button primary">Schedule a Visit</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>